def: The Evil Principle or Being of the ancient Persians; the Princeof Darkness as opposer to Ormuzd, the King of Light.
Resembling, or pertaining to, the iguana.
Capable of being constrained; liable to constraint, or torestraint. Hooker.
A white, amorphous, tenacious substance resembling caoutchouc,and obtained as an insoluble residue of mastic.
One who uses a sickle; a sickleman; a reaper.
